{
  "stem": "8.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, don't put your trust into the Russians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's God who will save us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I just had this faith.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was wonderful for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm sure that helped me survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And these men, you know, just-- even though they-- they didn't-- you know, they did not believe what I did, they wanted to hear it from me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They wanted me to say it to them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Maybe that helped them as well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We worked until-- well, it was Passover soon-- Passover.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And during Passover, we were already working just on and off because of the bombings.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And on Passover, I did not eat my allotted bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I-- I-- sometimes I got some potatoes, and I ate that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I don't know on which day, the fifth or sixth day, I just fainted from the-- from hunger, but was able to recover.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We all did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we were kind of-- we had all kinds of systems that we did.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had one woman who had a prayer book, who somehow got through-- got-- was able to save a prayer book, who used to, when we marched, she used to say it.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we used to say with her our prayers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was just amazing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You also had, of course, some problems with some of these women who were more religious than anybody, who didn't want to work on the sabbath.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and the daughter of our rabbi told them, you work just like the rest of us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You-- we-- even know though we are not allowed to work on Shabbat, this-- this time we all have to be the same place, and you cannot pull yourself away from the rest of us.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So these things happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
